The paper describes the development and validation of machine learning models to predict one-year mortality of patients based on data gathered at hospital admission. This involves the use of various machine learning techniques and evaluation metrics. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
